NNAAMMEE
       tbl-vert - vertical lines

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       no boxing:

       a   b
       c   d

       automatic boxing:

       +------+
       |a   b |
       |c   d |
       +------+
       manual boxing:

       +--++--+
       |a ||b |
       +--++--+
       |c ||d |
       +--++--+

       automatic and manual boxing:

       +--++--+
       |a ||b |
       +--++--+
       |c ||d |
       +--++--+


